00:36:27.167 --> 00:36:29.834
So we have a couple
of stories to end up here?

00:36:29.834 --> 00:36:32.767
Collins-Sussman:
Well, yeah. [laughs]

00:36:32.767 --> 00:36:38.200
Um, I think this is your story,
