00:40:36.300 --> 00:40:37.467
and that sort of thing.

00:40:37.467 --> 00:40:38.467
Collins-Sussman:
I guess I don't feel like

00:40:38.467 --> 00:40:39.968
it's a big paradigm shift.

00:40:39.968 --> 00:40:41.734
I mean, when I was a kid

00:40:41.734 --> 00:40:43.801
there were hardly
