technological things.

00:41:22.400 --> 00:41:23.734
I think we see that as--

00:41:23.734 --> 00:41:24.734
And I think that's more
of what your question was,

00:41:24.734 --> 00:41:25.734
if I understood.

00:41:25.734 --> 00:41:26.934
Collins-Sussman:
And more OCD.

00:41:26.934 --> 00:41:28.334
Fitzpatrick:
Yeah, and a little more OCD.

00:41:28.334 --> 00:41:29.801
And you're gonna see people
