which was two orders
of magnitude

00:42:58.601 --> 00:43:00.367
more than anybody
got at the time.

00:43:00.367 --> 00:43:02.734
And people really thought
it was an April Fool's joke

00:43:02.734 --> 00:43:03.968
five years ago
when they announced that.

